1. Log in to your chosen affiliate network (e.g., "AffiliateHub").
2. Search for the product you want to promote (e.g., "XYZ Fitness Tracker").
3. Click on the product listing.
4. Locate the "Generate Affiliate Link" button or similar option.
5. Copy the generated URL: `https://affiliatehub.com/xyzfitnesstracker?affid=YOURUNIQUEID`
